reviews.review_text: the beginning of a lifetime this was my first show,  halfway through the first set I was hooked

Fun show This was the last show the casinos ever let us in,Dead heads at the black Jack tables,they where not prepared for what they got when we showed up,I think Phoenix was the show right before and then the Who wild couple of days,another small place that was very nice,never saw the dead in a football stadium,kinda happy about that.Its Funny,seeing so many shows when you heard US Blues you would head for the door,oh what I would give now to hear Jerry play US blues I would sit still and take it in
